S.FORM: Eduard Heger Eduard Heger u siwkay niza u pilecuhan ni Eduard Heger i Bratislava nu Slovakia . nalecuhan ciniza i 5 a bulad 3 a demiad 1976 a mihcaan. pahezekay niza i tabakiay a cacudadan nu Bratislava (University of Economics in Bratislava ). micakat u cunli ( Prime Minister) nu Slovakia ayza sa ci Eduard Heger , micakat a demiad sa i 2021 a mihcaan 4 bulad 1 demiad. u ngangan niza u sulit tu ngangan nu Slovakia a kamu:Eduard Heger u sulit tu ngangan nu hulam a kamu: u sulit tu ngangan nu Sakizaya a kamu:Yikeel Matuwwyeci u sapuyaay a kakuniza kakuniza malalitin tu ihekalay atu zumaay a natinengan List of current heads of state and government Eduard Heger
